    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2026-03-16</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2026-04-03T15:02:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Grocery, Farm, and Food Worker Stabilization Grant Program Act of 2026</strong></p><p>This bill directs the Agricultural Marketing Service (AMS) to establish a grant program to provide&nbsp;farmworkers, meat processing workers, and grocery workers stabilization payments in the case of a natural disaster or other disaster. Specifically, AMS must provide funding to membership organizations or labor unions representing farmworkers, meat processing workers, and grocery workers for the payments.&nbsp;</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Grocery, Farm, and Food Worker Stabilization Grant Program Act of 2026</title>
